desc: Ocean View & 7th is a women's clothing boutique filled with wearable, beautiful, on trend styles that can take you from day-to-night; from the beach to girls night out; from work to a dinner date. With a wide selection and variety of styles; OV7 takes it's babes from Ocean View Blvd to 7th Avenue.

layout.text: Where Seventh Ave. Meets Ocean View Blvd.
Hand selected boutique clothing to take you from daytime to nightime, & everywhere between.
